Description: The rest on the flight into Egypt, the Virgin nurses the Christ Child at the left. Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Battista Angolo del Moro
Curator's comments: Bartsch notes the dependence of this composition on the work of Titian. This is a second state impression with the publishers mark. The verso of the sheet is coated with black chalk presumably for transfer.
Acquisition name: Purchased from: Charles Francis Arnold Howard, 5th Earl of Wicklow
